  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "oV0SUDvwD2VN8Gi9nlr2JZ2xcDrASmE2W5kc5SVX5eo=",
    "originContent": "## Installation",
    "translatedContent": "## 설치"
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "iYbrmqD1c4wb/BF38pBgmh6NkCT9QfwGkJ3+dKWxd90=",
    "originContent": "If you have previously installed Synology Drive Client with Alien or Flatpak (i.e. from another source than my repo), please ensure that they are uninstalled.",
    "translatedContent": "이전에 Alien 또는 Flatpak (즉, 제 저장소가 아닌 다른 출처)으로 Synology Drive 클라이언트를 설치한 경우, 반드시 제거했는지 확인하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "YKP4LaVNpx44vkhCvIdZGVwxCXVDf2WH1aAA2sNZix4=",
    "originContent": "If you like the project, do not hesitate to star the repository to support me, thank you!",
    "translatedContent": "프로젝트가 마음에 들면, 저를 지원하기 위해 저장소에 별점을 주는 것을 망설이지 마세요, 감사합니다!"
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "V10LkSuAw992ip8fCTN7GLK+A1spqdibCAMwBTOKdfI=",
    "originContent": "### Method 1: install from COPR repo (recommended to get updates)",
    "translatedContent": "### 방법 1: COPR 저장소에서 설치 (업데이트를 받기에 권장)"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "TWTj8zbAi6wh5/P8f1gsEZKS24MsxqvzQHna3jsOFHU=",
    "originContent": "Page link : [COPR package](https://copr.fedorainfracloud.org/coprs/emixampp/synology-drive/).",
    "translatedContent": "페이지 링크 : [COPR 패키지](https://copr.fedorainfracloud.org/coprs/emixampp/synology-drive/)."
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "aNBRN1yj+0tfzq7xFz4xZBo6h7rCNZetQ2onTJ4gUYk=",
    "originContent": "1. `sudo dnf copr enable emixampp/synology-drive`",
    "translatedContent": "1. `sudo dnf copr enable emixampp/synology-drive`"
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "qHRIAXiXkFBNh1rirx/6T5FuYUvUBIqHZL5XnB10bXc=",
    "originContent": "2. For GNOME: `sudo dnf --refresh install synology-drive`",
    "translatedContent": "2. GNOME용: `sudo dnf --refresh install synology-drive`"
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "1KPNmVPhYsj+zUNFacUeGJh9/c50sgRy8Z05ZoAZRQU=",
    "originContent": "3. For other desktop environments: `sudo dnf --refresh install synology-drive-noextra`",
    "translatedContent": "3. 다른 데스크탑 환경용: `sudo dnf --refresh install synology-drive-noextra`"
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "Mzv+lthB3iHf7WUraqu/M7ybnBc8GvKxKbZvv9dgTTI=",
    "originContent": "### Method 2: build the package locally (no update)",
    "translatedContent": "### 방법 2: 로컬에서 패키지 빌드 (업데이트 없음)"
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "4iFTLDW4yD096eAPgRtBaaqtKt9lxQt/oaEg+Z04BnI=",
    "originContent": "1. Install build tools : `sudo dnf install rpm-build rpmdevtools`",
    "translatedContent": "1. 빌드 도구 설치 : `sudo dnf install rpm-build rpmdevtools`"
  },
  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "344J1bfrrJcfbv7G/5qJCWb+dQjukNOOyVtAQClqxZ0=",
    "originContent": "2. `git clone https://github.com/EmixamPP/synology-drive.git`",
    "translatedContent": "2. `git clone https://github.com/EmixamPP/synology-drive.git`"
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "brp8nw63gALkeQz6PqX+hlkQpo4I0+VrfF2GnSLVfQI=",
    "originContent": "3. `cd synology-drive`",
    "translatedContent": "3. `cd synology-drive`"
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "7LN86qeNTNkjjHsjT6IsssCpC4982MRHkCDY8yPveRo=",
    "originContent": "4. Optional, if you want to change the version:",
    "translatedContent": "4. 선택 사항, 버전을 변경하고 싶다면:"
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "kEm5B0z/mRp72FaXUs41mGA5Zwyev36+BlpWjWlsE94=",
    "originContent": "   1. Consult the [release notes](https://www.synology.com/en-global/releaseNote/SynologyDriveClient) and choose the desired version (>= 3.2.1-13271)",
    "translatedContent": "   1. [릴리즈 노트](https://www.synology.com/en-global/releaseNote/SynologyDriveClient)를 확인하고 원하는 버전(>= 3.2.1-13271)을 선택하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "CAkEU+fjVB/JPBTzIOIy6FoPzRAQ6kpNQXSfghTHTgQ=",
    "originContent": "   2. Edit the two first lines of `synology-drive.spec` or `synology-drive-noextra.spec`, depending on whether you are running GNOME or another desktop environement. ",
    "translatedContent": "   2. GNOME을 사용하는지 다른 데스크탑 환경인지에 따라 `synology-drive.spec` 또는 `synology-drive-noextra.spec`의 처음 두 줄을 편집하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "an/m1kyFKK8FhsHtvdaNfohUoT8glo3H6vKiEnAXqe4=",
    "originContent": "5. For GNOME:",
    "translatedContent": "5. GNOME용:"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "oFi0Uyad2K+idMl83Xs8o/pvj4Ud+AfaVcrB1hZ9hRY=",
    "originContent": "   1. `spectool -g -R synology-drive.spec`",
    "translatedContent": "   1. `spectool -g -R synology-drive.spec`"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "H3qiUMdyH+3wINXyNg9iuEtdTUyfamVHX00aPC7/pV4=",
    "originContent": "   2. `rpmbuild -ba synology-drive.spec`",
    "translatedContent": "   2. `rpmbuild -ba synology-drive.spec`"
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "JYGriG2/keOBWZ7BIHSD5809VS6wHPhNV+4uofCUqXY=",
    "originContent": "   3. `sudo dnf install ~/rpmbuild/RPMS/x86_64/synology-drive-*.x86_64.rpm`",
    "translatedContent": "   3. `sudo dnf install ~/rpmbuild/RPMS/x86_64/synology-drive-*.x86_64.rpm`"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "Fvw6X7CSm6UAqcDUwDDfoqCYlVAWFqQBRTAXIelgsns=",
    "originContent": "6. For other desktop environments: ",
    "translatedContent": "6. 다른 데스크탑 환경용:"
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "oYB8eUMxax69sXBIfRoLuSlibcQ+cY6lu/TvbRAIRag=",
    "originContent": "   1. `spectool -g -R synology-drive-noextra.spec`",
    "translatedContent": "   1. `spectool -g -R synology-drive-noextra.spec`"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "XZAGDgl1uTt14yO6VPcMQitOxrcfChmA/0r6MOc66lU=",
    "originContent": "   2. `rpmbuild -ba synology-drive-noextra.spec`",
    "translatedContent": "   2. `rpmbuild -ba synology-drive-noextra.spec`"
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "odn/DK3PIzr2ew297na9ZM1EDlEbET0FYlz9ZQpmOuo=",
    "originContent": "   3. `sudo dnf install ~/rpmbuild/RPMS/x86_64/synology-drive-noextra-*.x86_64.rpm`",
    "translatedContent": "   3. `sudo dnf install ~/rpmbuild/RPMS/x86_64/synology-drive-noextra-*.x86_64.rpm`"
  },
  {
